Package: tsclient
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, rdesktop (>= 1.9.0)
Description: Terminal Server Client for Linux desktops
 Terminal Server Client (tsclient) is a GTK4 frontend for rdesktop, VNC viewers,
 and other remote desktop tools. It provides JSON-based profile storage, a
 Cinnamon panel applet for recent connections, and modern GTK4 UI components.
